  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbbreviationLookup
    Used to lookup and verify abbreviations that are found as potential participantAs
    ChEMBLLookup
    Used to lookup specific word types in the larger chembl database
    ChemicalLookup
    Lookup for terms in the Chebi database.
    IPILookup
    Used to lookup proteins that are given in the old IPI format
    Lookup
    Abstract Class for protein lookups
    SpeciesChecker
    This class is not currently used, but it can create a lookup for species deemed invalid.
    SuffixLookup
    Creates a lookup of suffixes for potential drugs.
    TabLookup
    Lookup table for grounding entities that are mammal.
    YeastLookup
    Lookup table for grounding entities that are mammal.
